OL,3,CMan denies murder after pedestrians
OL,4,Chit by car in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a non-
OL,7,Fleague footballer and also pleaded not
OL,8,Fguilty to attempting to murder five
OL,9,Fother men, after a group of people
OL,10,Fwere hit by a car in Arnold,
OL,11,FNottinghamshire.
OL,13,FDuane Anthony will face trial at
OL,14,FNottingham Crown Court in October
OL,15,Faccused of the murder of Tyler
OL,16,FFairman, who played for
OL,17,FNottinghamshire-based Woodthorpe Park
OL,18,FRangers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
