CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782778699
OL,3,CMan denies murder after pedestrians
OL,4,Chit by car in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FMr Fairman, aged 26, died in hospital
OL,7,Fin May, three days after a group of
OL,8,Fpedestrians was hit by a Vauxhall
OL,9,FAstra car in Market Place, Arnold,
OL,10,Fnear Nottingham.
OL,12,FAppearing in court by video-link from
OL,13,FHMP Manchester on Monday, Anthony, of
OL,14,FMarton Road, Bulwell, spoke only to
OL,15,Fenter pleas and to confirm his name
OL,16,Fduring an 18-minute hearing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782778699
OL,3,CMan denies murder after pedestrians
OL,4,Chit by car in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FDefence barrister Sue Rodham told the
OL,7,Fcourt Anthony did not dispute being
OL,8,Fthe driver of the car, but had "no
OL,9,Fintention to kill or to cause really
OL,10,Fserious bodily harm".
OL,12,FNumerous friends and relatives of Mr
OL,13,FFairman watched proceedings from the
OL,14,Fpublic gallery as Anthony pleaded not
OL,15,Fguilty to murder and five counts of
OL,16,Fattempted murder. He also denied a
OL,17,Fcharge of driving while disqualified.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
