PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782778699
OL,3,CMan denies murder after pedestrians
OL,4,Chit by car in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FAdjourning the case, Recorder of
OL,7,FNottingham Judge Nirmal Shant KC told
OL,8,FAnthony: "As far as you are concerned,
OL,9,Fyour trial is listed for October 7.
OL,11,F"But there is to be a listing before
OL,12,Fthen on September 2 that is designed
OL,13,Fto ensure that everything is in place
OL,14,Ffor the trial to be effective."
OL,16,FWoodthorpe Park Rangers has previously
OL,17,Fsaid that three members of its team,
OL,18,Fincluding the manager, were struck by
OL,19,Fa car following an end-of-season
OL,20,Fawards night.
OL,26,@pD@JOUsD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
