CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782778699
OL,3,CMan denies murder after pedestrians
OL,4,Chit by car in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FIn a tribute issued shortly after his
OL,7,Fdeath, Mr Fairman's family said:
OL,8,F"There are no words now, nor will
OL,9,Fthere ever be, to truly describe how
OL,10,Fbroken this has left us all.
OL,12,F"Our hearts are shattered, and the
OL,13,Fworld has become a much darker place
OL,14,Fwithout him in it."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUvD@SO]
